The State Tribunal has withdrawn.

00:32:14.912 --> 00:32:16.039
Your Highness.

00:32:20.126 --> 00:32:21.961
Have we found the assassin yet?

00:32:22.045 --> 00:32:25.882
I still suspect
Lord Hong Min-jik's family.

00:32:30.720 --> 00:32:32.430
Really? That family?

00:32:33.181 --> 00:32:36.768
Min-jik's eldest son doesn't have the guts
or the skills to do that.

00:32:36.851 --> 00:32:39.145
The other one is his concubine's daughter.

00:32:39.228 --> 00:32:41.481
I hear the number of arrows
His Majesty used in this hunt

00:32:41.564 --> 00:32:43.232
exceeds those used in the Eulmyo War.

00:32:44.275 --> 00:32:48.154
His Majesty's arrows are scattered
all around the Royal Villa unretrieved.

00:32:50.156 --> 00:32:51.199
Should we interrogate

00:32:51.282 --> 00:32:53.785
all thousands of people
cast out of Chungcheong?

00:32:56.245 --> 00:32:58.372
I hear Grand Prince Dowol woke up.
Go and talk to him.

00:32:58.956 --> 00:33:01.084
He made his move
knowing the assassin's plan.

00:33:01.167 --> 00:33:02.710
He must have had a source.

00:33:03.836 --> 00:33:04.962
Let me go and talk to him.

00:33:05.546 --> 00:33:07.840
We're not on good terms,
but I've talked to him before.

00:33:09.550 --> 00:33:11.177
Just make up some excuse.

00:33:12.261 --> 00:33:15.264
Say I lost my memory from the shock,
or something along those lines.

00:33:17.517 --> 00:33:19.185
I'm not in the mood for jokes.

00:33:19.268 --> 00:33:21.187
You don't joke because you're in the mood.

00:33:21.270 --> 00:33:22.688
You joke to get in the mood.

00:33:26.067 --> 00:33:27.735
"The Gyeongo Year was not forgotten."

00:33:27.819 --> 00:33:30.947
Tell him that message
was put up in the market again.

00:33:31.030 --> 00:33:33.241
He's always under threat of assassination,

00:33:33.741 --> 00:33:35.034
so you make up the rest.

00:33:36.327 --> 00:33:37.912
So you're ordering me around now?

00:33:38.913 --> 00:33:40.540
We want to protect the same person.

00:33:41.791 --> 00:33:43.543
It's a strategic alliance.

00:33:45.378 --> 00:33:47.004
Since we're on the same side,

00:33:49.590 --> 00:33:50.716
we could be friends too.

00:33:55.054 --> 00:33:56.264
That would be difficult.

00:33:58.141 --> 00:33:59.392
I told Hong Eun-jo

00:34:00.893 --> 00:34:03.396
who struck Your Highness with the arrow.

00:34:05.815 --> 00:34:08.401
She's already overwhelmed with grief now.

00:34:08.484 --> 00:34:10.653
- Why did you do that?
- She needs to know.

00:34:10.736 --> 00:34:13.322
She needs to know
where her anger was directed

00:34:14.073 --> 00:34:17.118
so she won't make a foolish choice
like taking her own life.

00:34:18.077 --> 00:34:19.871
And she will walk away.

00:34:19.954 --> 00:34:23.332
Once she sees
where this wretched tie leads,

00:34:25.418 --> 00:34:27.128
she will have to walk away.

00:34:29.547 --> 00:34:30.673
So…

00:34:31.507 --> 00:34:33.092
I hope you recover soon.

00:34:34.302 --> 00:34:36.804
I'm saying this as someone
who was briefly your friend.

00:34:39.849 --> 00:34:43.352
HYEMINSEO

00:35:12.340 --> 00:35:14.217
Go. I don't need that.

00:35:14.300 --> 00:35:15.468
That's none of your concern.

00:35:49.126 --> 00:35:51.420
It looks like you're in a hurry.

00:35:51.504 --> 00:35:53.214
If you're making a house call…

00:35:53.881 --> 00:35:55.925
I was on my way to see you.

00:35:59.011 --> 00:36:00.888
I guess I'm a little late.

00:36:03.975 --> 00:36:05.851
Shall we step inside for a bit?

00:36:07.895 --> 00:36:09.230
About that day…

00:36:09.313 --> 00:36:10.648
Don't worry about it.

00:36:12.984 --> 00:36:14.026
I came to say this.

00:36:24.912 --> 00:36:26.247
I'm fine.

00:36:26.872 --> 00:36:29.542
The royal physician said
that I had a naturally strong heart.

00:36:53.357 --> 00:36:54.358
See?

00:36:55.860 --> 00:36:57.236
It's beating.

00:37:24.305 --> 00:37:25.765
It must have

00:37:26.515 --> 00:37:27.683
hurt so much.

00:37:31.604 --> 00:37:32.438
Not at all.

00:37:35.191 --> 00:37:37.151
I was just glad

00:37:37.234 --> 00:37:39.070
the arrow struck here.

00:38:00.299 --> 00:38:01.592
I'm sorry.

00:38:04.303 --> 00:38:05.513
I'm really

00:38:06.764 --> 00:38:08.099
sorry.

00:38:48.764 --> 00:38:50.474
Are you going to stay out here all night?

00:38:52.309 --> 00:38:53.727
I'm thinking about

00:38:54.895 --> 00:38:57.273
how I can dry her tears.

00:39:27.178 --> 00:39:28.804
What are you doing?

00:39:30.181 --> 00:39:31.098
Recovery workout.

00:39:31.599 --> 00:39:33.601
I happened to come across a sturdy tree.

00:39:33.684 --> 00:39:35.102
Bye then.

00:39:56.707 --> 00:39:58.542
I came across another sturdy tree.

00:39:59.251 --> 00:40:00.794
Bye then.

00:40:16.810 --> 00:40:18.187
You finished early.

00:40:18.854 --> 00:40:20.606
He said he wanted to learn some skills.

00:40:25.069 --> 00:40:26.529
Can we talk?

00:40:30.574 --> 00:40:31.575
What is it?

00:40:32.117 --> 00:40:33.744
What are you going to nag me about?

00:40:40.459 --> 00:40:41.794
I know

00:40:42.503 --> 00:40:43.337
what you're doing.

00:40:47.466 --> 00:40:48.592
I got the message.

00:40:54.306 --> 00:40:55.724
Was it too obvious?

00:40:59.186 --> 00:41:00.688
Don't overdo it.

00:41:04.233 --> 00:41:07.027
Even if it's obvious, just buy it.

00:41:07.444 --> 00:41:09.154
Just play along

00:41:10.030 --> 00:41:13.450
and forget who you shot that day.

00:41:15.578 --> 00:41:17.454
I know you can't forget
what happened that day,

00:41:19.498 --> 00:41:21.083
and you probably shouldn't,

00:41:23.335 --> 00:41:24.962
but at least forget that part.

00:41:26.171 --> 00:41:27.923
At least just this part.

00:41:31.760 --> 00:41:33.512
If you promise me that,

00:41:34.054 --> 00:41:35.764
I'll stop telling such obvious lies.

00:41:44.773 --> 00:41:45.941
I promise.

00:41:49.320 --> 00:41:50.237
I'll try to forget.

00:41:57.286 --> 00:41:59.788
RESPECTED GENTLEMEN OF THE NAMYANG
HONG CLAN - TONGJEONG DAEBU

00:42:05.336 --> 00:42:06.920
What I did was wrong.

00:42:17.139 --> 00:42:20.434
Once you draw the bowstring,
hold your breath.

00:42:20.517 --> 00:42:23.562
Even the gentlest breeze
can sway an arrow.

00:42:28.317 --> 00:42:31.403
Once you draw the bowstring,
still your emotions.

00:42:31.820 --> 00:42:34.823
Even the slightest sadness
can make an arrow veer.

00:42:37.826 --> 00:42:40.537
I'm scared, my lord.

00:42:41.664 --> 00:42:42.873
What if

00:42:43.666 --> 00:42:46.335
I end up hurting someone?

00:42:47.961 --> 00:42:51.799
Swords and bows are not for hurting.

00:42:52.383 --> 00:42:54.259
They're for protecting.

00:42:57.137 --> 00:42:59.056
I was blinded by my anger

00:42:59.682 --> 00:43:02.101
and I ended up doing the same thing

00:43:02.184 --> 00:43:04.144
the king did to you, Father.

00:43:07.106 --> 00:43:08.607
I deserve your scolding.

00:43:32.005 --> 00:43:34.508
When can we see His Majesty?

00:43:35.509 --> 00:43:38.178
His Majesty's heart
has been troubled lately. Please wait.

00:43:38.262 --> 00:43:41.390
Rumor has it that His Majesty isn't well.

00:43:44.935 --> 00:43:48.230
I hope that's not what you're wishing for.

00:43:48.689 --> 00:43:50.023
That's absurd.

00:43:50.858 --> 00:43:51.692
All I meant was

00:43:51.775 --> 00:43:54.403
that you shouldn't be solely in charge,
if that's the case.

00:44:06.248 --> 00:44:08.417
He raised concerns about the damage

00:44:08.500 --> 00:44:11.837
His Majesty's hunting and parties
caused the people.

00:44:13.172 --> 00:44:17.092
And that infuriated His Majesty.

00:44:19.178 --> 00:44:20.471
Until the very end,

00:44:22.598 --> 00:44:23.974
he stayed true to himself.

00:44:29.396 --> 00:44:32.441
As you said, Lord Hong Min-jik

00:44:32.524 --> 00:44:35.194
was a subject
who gave only honest and necessary advice.

00:44:36.111 --> 00:44:39.072
All the subjects who challenged
His Majesty had been killed,

00:44:40.532 --> 00:44:42.743
but he kept Lord Hong alive.

00:44:49.333 --> 00:44:50.751
As you know, it's because

00:44:51.919 --> 00:44:53.879
he was both the teacher
and friend of His Majesty.

00:44:58.133 --> 00:44:59.676
Are you sure that was the only reason?

00:45:01.887 --> 00:45:05.140
I wouldn't dare lie to you, Your Highness.

00:45:07.351 --> 00:45:08.560
How's the king?

00:45:10.312 --> 00:45:12.689
I heard he's still asleep.

00:45:15.275 --> 00:45:18.278
Something is happening in his bedchamber.

00:45:18.820 --> 00:45:20.864
What could it be?

00:45:23.200 --> 00:45:24.701
How is he?

00:45:25.577 --> 00:45:26.954
He perks up briefly,

00:45:27.538 --> 00:45:30.082
then falls asleep after each meal
as the medicine takes effect.

00:45:34.503 --> 00:45:36.213
What happened on the hunting trip

00:45:36.797 --> 00:45:39.091
must never be revealed to anyone.

00:45:41.718 --> 00:45:44.179
They are your people, Your Majesty.

00:45:44.263 --> 00:45:45.973
Please take pity on them.

00:46:00.779 --> 00:46:03.574
That's enough. You're ruining my mood.

00:46:08.328 --> 00:46:11.665
Min-jik, go back to the capital
and wait for my command.

00:46:15.419 --> 00:46:17.671
Let's begin the hunt!

00:47:08.138 --> 00:47:09.723
It's a tiger.

00:47:18.607 --> 00:47:20.984
Bring the tiger I hunted!

00:47:52.057 --> 00:47:54.976
The herb can cause
visual and auditory hallucinations?

00:47:55.060 --> 00:47:57.145
How could you not tell me that?

00:47:57.979 --> 00:48:00.732
Tomorrow, he could see me as a fox
and hunt me too!

00:48:00.816 --> 00:48:03.735
And that would be too honorable a death
for a lowlife like you.

00:48:07.948 --> 00:48:10.242
Send the body to Min-jik's son

00:48:10.659 --> 00:48:12.411
and give him a horse.

00:48:15.247 --> 00:48:18.792
I guess I forgot my place for a moment.

00:48:30.429 --> 00:48:32.514
Let the king lie there

00:48:33.265 --> 00:48:35.600
and become a living corpse.

00:48:37.644 --> 00:48:39.771
Don't worry.

00:49:11.845 --> 00:49:12.929
Now,

00:49:14.181 --> 00:49:15.974
come back to this place of torment.

00:49:26.651 --> 00:49:29.946
Everything you saw and heard here
must remain completely secret.

00:49:31.823 --> 00:49:32.949
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

00:49:42.626 --> 00:49:44.169
Because that secret ends with you.

00:49:46.546 --> 00:49:47.380
It's done. (Support Admin Watch on
